{"title":"有个名字最闪亮","authors":["陈世禄"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":6,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"有个名字最闪亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈世禄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在抗击非典的战场上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有个名字最闪亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这名字下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集合着无数的先锋战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数不清的优秀儿郎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是百姓的知音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是人民的希望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是国家的中流砥柱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是民族的臂膀脊梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像战鼓，向SARS擂起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似号角，向病魔吹响；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像阳光，温暖着生命；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似雨露，滋润着心房；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像旗帜，凝聚人心力量；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似丰碑，铭刻时代辉煌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我是共产党员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是人民的儿郎。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“在最危难的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党员我不上谁上。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这发自肺腑的声音呐喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从心底迸发的誓言力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战死神，灭非典，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷霆万钧般铿锵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在抗击非典的战场上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党员——名字最闪亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是因为，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党人："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心底最无私，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精神最高尚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"性格最执著，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意志最坚强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸怀最宽阔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情意最深长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目标最远大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理想最令人向往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗帜最鲜艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生最壮丽辉煌……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":10,"page_end":10}